Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:24.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,Culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Culprit".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.45,0:00:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever there is a crime, there is a culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in order to cover up their crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they'll stop at nothing to try and deceive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, the surprising identity of the culprit\Nwho targeted Sonoko is revealed,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as we play back\N"Sonoko's Dangerous Summer Tale (Part 2)"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If we keep mourning the passing seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:46.31,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}we can't confront the mysteries in cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:50.12,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Big trouble by the summer seaside!\NThe mysterious man in front of Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.27,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.27,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:56.57,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.53,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The three of us went to Izu to do some swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.16,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran and I are witness to a strange summer event!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.87,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:30.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko gets herself a boyfriend. His name is Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.47,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But while she's in seventh heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:36.34,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}waiting for him to pick her up for their dinner date,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.94,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}someone attacks her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:48.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it my imagination, or are we being watched?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:53.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What bothers me is that man\Nwith the glasses who Ran saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:57.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the man who attacked Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:02:59.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is he really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}just a burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a lovely restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There don't seem to be\Nmany customers, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we came too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you aren't coming, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was up all night thinking about that burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll rest in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right. But what a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are drinks in this cooler, so help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll see you later, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After your nap and if you're feeling up to it, join us in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think she'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's sleeping inside a hot car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I turned the air conditioner on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this for one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's plenty and the price is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the secret to this restaurant's success!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:42.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh brother, a full-course meal for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:04:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you the food was great?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm completely stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel a bit bad for Sonoko though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're from the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's your brown-haired friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't get enough sleep last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she's resting in the car parked outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that your car, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why's it moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's heading straight for a cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where do you think you're going? Pay your bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:02.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's a lock pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:10.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The side brake's disengaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, wake up! Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't put full strength in while I'm running!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, let go of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, grab onto me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you guys all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you put the side brakes on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! I {\i1}did{\i0} have them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they weren't on, the car would've fallen off the cliff a lot sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone released the side brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone broke into the car using a lock pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who wanted Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So someone broke into the car while Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was asleep inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and released the side brake,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and made it roll down this slope and off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the diver's report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The side brakes of the car\Nunderwater were disengaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, we found this lying on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been wiped clean of prints!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a puddle of water that must've\Nleaked out of the car's air conditioner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where the car was parked in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, did you notice any\Nsuspicious figures around the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't sleep much last night,\Nso I was sound asleep in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But ever since we arrived in Izu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we're being followed for some unknown reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's him over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind identifying yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I work at the inn where the girls are staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came here today to have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inn's not busy during the afternoon, and I had some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He isn't behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:03.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When the car started moving, he was already in the restaurant with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he'd forced the car door open,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:12.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}released the side brake, and\Nthen come into the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:16.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}we would have seen him walk in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:22.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The waiter told me that the back door is always kept locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:27.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We first noticed him when he came out of the restroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:31.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but there's no window leading out from inside the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And of course, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s in the clear too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:40.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He was eating with us and never left the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:47.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The most likely suspect is the man following us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is he anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll take all your statements down at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please get into the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, I don't feel like riding in a car just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about I walk you to the police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that far, and we can\Nenjoy the scenery. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if she gets attacked again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} does have brown{light} hair, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her assailant could also be the killer from that other case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would be foolish enough to attack her in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But you never know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will be with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and so will Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just don't stop anywhere.\NCome straight to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, man...{old: I can't believe it.I *think* Viz had 'But still...'?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The attack at the inn last night,\Nand then the car incident today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sure are after you.{What's with you anyway?gonbe suggestions: You sure have bad luck. - Just why is this all happening to you. Viz had lol: Danger seems to stick to you like GLUE.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, are you sure you\Ndon't know what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because you're so charming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right, why is she being targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:20.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And if he wanted her dead, why didn't he do it when he broke into the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:28.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There was no need for the car to be pushed off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We planned on leaving Izu as soon as we had lunch, so all of our luggage was in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've all gone up in flames now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, why is all of this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might've lost your\Nluggage, but I lost my {\i1}car{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because you got involved with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I brought you bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not so unlucky. You lost all your memorable photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something you can never replace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that's left now is that one photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, the one I'm going to show Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have it on me at all times—\Nyou have nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still have it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, get rid of it! You're making me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! It's that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:22.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He wants to get rid of that photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:27.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He had to send the car over the cliff to get rid of her luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:31.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:36.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why does he think Sonoko took an incriminating picture of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:42.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There wasn't a single unusual photo in the bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:47.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or did I overlook something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we're being followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it more dangerous to go through the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is more thrilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's split up to shake him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:44.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he's Sonoko's attacker, why's he still after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All the photos were burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:52.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A train?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:56.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, they found a body in this forest yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:01.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When we passed this place a couple nights ago, I'm sure a train went by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:05.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm missing something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! I've lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The situation's turning bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you thought we'd just run, you're sadly mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have run\Nthrough the forest in sandals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:45.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sandals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who attacked Sonoko last night at the inn, and sent the car over the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on there! That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No use lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your hairy arms are proof enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should be bite marks where Sonoko bit you last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? It can't be... No bite marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe on the other arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? No marks on this arm either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective with the Chiba\NPrefecture Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just showing me the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think I'd fall for that trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father used to be a police officer. You can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When an officer has to identify him or herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they must show the first page of the police notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the photo and corresponding data.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoji Terabayashi at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. It's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm on the trail of a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't usually wear socks with sandals, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:58.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stepped on a twig.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess running about in the forest\Nwith sandals wasn't such a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tooth marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be so\Nsurprised about, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the mark you gave me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I finally get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:46.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko didn't bite an arm last night, but his leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:47.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She must've gotten mixed up in the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:51.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He thought Sonoko took his picture
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}because the sparks the train's pantograph{?!} produces
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}lit his back at the time of the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:04.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}when Sonoko passed by holding a camera,\Nand he jumped to the wrong conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He thought there'd be a shot of him with the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:11.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, I remember him saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:15.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't worry. You look good in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:17.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yukata, swimsuit, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:22.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The only time Sonoko wore a yukata was during the fireworks show two nights ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We only met him yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How could he know what\Nshe looks like in a yukata?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:28.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:29.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why didn't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why didn't I figure it out sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The picture you were going to have some detective look at!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably thought you took a romantic picture of a couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I was in the middle of committing murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} killed four people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was responsible for the murder the other night,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then she's probably the fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, he only\Nkills girls with brown{light} hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had my eyes on him for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got him on a stolen vehicle charge once,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there wasn't enough\Nproof on the murder charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to Izu because I heard that a similar murder happened there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I arrived too late to save his latest victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's something I still don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did he make the car move on its own if he was in the restaurant the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took a wedge-shaped piece of ice out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and placed it under the left front tyre to prevent it from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he pretended to talk to Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} who was inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and released the side brake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he left a lock pick on the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to divert the investigation!{would "as a red herring" be too far out in left field here? XD}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he left two spaces open when he parked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there'd be no cars obstructing his car's path when it moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, the melted ice would just appear to be water from the AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:12.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why does he kill only girls with brown hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?\NA heartless girl dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever I see flirty girls like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Girls with brown hair, just like the one who dumped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over there! Isn't that Sonoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:35.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:42.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why are all the guys that make a play for me so weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I hate you, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am {\i1}I{\i0} all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd seen that guy with the glasses before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was at the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the captain of the Haido High School Karate Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Prince of Kicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto Kyogoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a very reckless lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lucky I was nearby and had some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Free time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mean you were\Nfollowing me all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was following you the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I lost sight of you in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew you might mistake me for a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:21:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'd been flirting with a few other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It got me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you worry about me? You don't even know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably didn't notice me, but I'd seen you once before, at a karate tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were cheering on your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd\Nreserve a room in our inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suggest you stop wearing\Noutfits that are too revealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It arouses the guys more than necessary.
